    <item>
      <title>低评级 CLO ETF 规模首次超过 10 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/janus-henderson-etf-aimed-at-low-rated-clos-surpasses-1-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一只购买低评级担保贷款债务（CLO）敞口的交易所交易基金的资产规模已超过 10 亿美元，这对于曾经仅对机构投资者开放的市场中快速增长的 CLO 基金而言又是一个里程碑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/janus-henderson-etf-aimed-at-low-rated-clos-surpasses-1-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 13:11:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>银行强烈反对后欧洲央行将推迟公布杠杆贷款调查结果</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/ecb-is-set-to-delay-findings-of-leveraged-loans-probe-after-backlash-from-banks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行将推迟公布针对高风险贷款的大规模调查结果，这意味着该行默认其认为多家银行对该调查的抱怨是合理的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/ecb-is-set-to-delay-findings-of-leveraged-loans-probe-after-backlash-from-banks</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 11:51:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苹果被摩根士丹利评为首选股 再创历史新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/apple-is-top-pick-at-morgan-stanley-as-ai-seen-driving-iphone-ipad-upgrades</link>
      <description><![CDATA[苹果公司 (Apple Inc.) 周一再创新高，此前这家科技巨头被摩根士丹利 (Morgan Stanley) 列为首选股票。摩根士丹利认为，苹果人工智能平台的推出引发了用户升级智能手机、平板电脑和电脑的新一轮热潮。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/apple-is-top-pick-at-morgan-stanley-as-ai-seen-driving-iphone-ipad-upgrades</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 11:01:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>克利夫兰克利夫斯公司将以 28 亿美元收购加拿大 Stelco 公司</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/cleveland-cliffs-to-buy-rival-stelco-for-c-3-85-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[克利夫兰-克利夫斯公司 (Cleveland-Cliffs Inc.) 同意以约 38.5 亿加元（28 亿美元）收购加拿大钢铁制造商 Stelco Holdings Inc.，这是该公司在去年竞购美国钢铁公司失败后的首次重大举措。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/cleveland-cliffs-to-buy-rival-stelco-for-c-3-85-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 10:14:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尼日利亚顶级银行计划出售 2.46 亿美元股份以获取资本</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/top-nigeria-lender-plans-246-million-share-sale-to-boost-gtbank</link>
      <description><![CDATA[担保信托控股公司 (Guaranty Trust Holding Co.) 计划通过出售股票筹集 2.462 亿美元，为其尼日利亚子公司注入更多资本，这是自 3 月份尼日利亚央行提高该行业的资本门槛以来，贷款机构最关注的一家公司。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/top-nigeria-lender-plans-246-million-share-sale-to-boost-gtbank</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 09:36:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
